dmca.title: Brightcove ID's Allegedly Infringing Downloads
dmca.body:
Files within the Brightcove account named 'Pax Stereo' have recently been identified as containing copyright protected material.  As a result, the file(s) listed below have been disabled and will be deleted in 5 business days.  If you believe you have appropriate rights to use and distribute the file(s) through the Brightcove Service and wish to prevent the deletion of the file(s), please review the FAQ [http://studio.brightcove.com/library/faq/copyright_flag_faq.cfm] for next steps.  You can also refer to the Brightcove Terms and Conditions, available at http://www.brightcove.com/legal/terms_general.cfm.

1. 'cominbackagain.flv' (Asset ID 488098951) : The song 'Comin' Back Again' by The Hemsley-Foster Project from the album 'Live @ Nyala's' (Pax Stereo; 02-Aug-2005) was identified.

2. 'funny.flv' (Asset ID 488217188) : The song 'Funny' by The Hemsley-Foster Project from the album 'Live @ Nyala's' (Pax Stereo; 02-Aug-2005) was identified.
